Completes the domain-based restructure by migrating products, suppliers, invites, bootstrap, and health into their own packages. Extracts seed data from bootstrap logic into a dedicated seed_data.py. Removes the now-empty api, schemas, and services directories. After this PR, every domain is self-contained: {domain}/routes.py, {domain}/schemas.py, {domain}/service.py.

